Single paragraph, plain text.
```
hello world
.
hello world
```

Soft line breaks collapse to a space.
```
line one
line two
line three
.
line one line two line three
```

Two paragraphs separated by a blank line.
```
first paragraph

second paragraph
.
first paragraph

second paragraph
```

Hard line break (backslash + newline).
```
first\
second
.
first
second
```
